153
00:06:44.145 --> 00:06:46.125
if you've got a sitting week, it is a sitting week,

154
00:06:46.265 --> 00:06:48.125
and if you've got a recess week, it is a recess week.

155
00:06:48.125 --> 00:06:49.525
